title: Zwoen - Zenith EP (2015)
description:
RELEASE	      2015-06-19
LABELS	      Trebuchet Music
CATALOGUE #   TRBM004
QUALITY       320kbit/s mp3
GENRE         Deep House, Electronic


The Zenith EP tells the story about a journey to a personal destination, with its initial ambitions, but also appearing issues on the way. Early Bird describes the beginning of the journey. Starting the task with inexperience, you'll soon get overwhelmed by all the impressions. This is illustrated by the songs rapid pace and alternating arpeggio sounds. Coming to the second half of the track, you get more and more calmed as you try to concentrate on the actual goal of yours. Morgenrot with its up-tempo beat, cheerful main melody and usage of bright instruments, depicts the successful overcoming of first difficulties. Now, everything seems to happen by itself. Unfortunately, this situation doesn't last long, as in Fierce new problems and even bigger obstacles impede the way to the goal. It impends that everything will break apart. A heavy bassline and distorted sounds visualize the biggest challenge yet. Finally, with the end in sight, you get pumped with new energy. With its euphoric samples and synthesizers as well as a dubstep-like beat and bassline, Tilt attends you on the last steps to the zenith
